<view class="page status-page"><view class="{{['status-banner-card', f]}}"><view class="status-icon-wrap"><image class="status-icon-image" src="{{a}}" mode="aspectFit"/></view><view class="status-banner-meta"><view class="status-title-text">{{b}}</view><view class="status-subtitle-text"><text wx:if="{{c}}">恭喜！您的资质已通过审核，可立即找车交易。</text><text wx:elif="{{d}}">提交成功，客服将在1-2个工作日内完成审核。</text><text wx:elif="{{e}}">您的申请未能通过审核，请修改后重新提交。</text><text wx:else>您还未提交车商身份认证，无法搜索或交易。</text></view></view></view><view wx:if="{{g}}" class="section reject-reason-card"><view class="reject-title">驳回原因</view><view class="reject-body">{{h}}</view></view><view wx:if="{{i}}" class="section info-card"><view class="section-title">认证材料档案</view><view class="info-list"><view class="info-row-item"><text class="row-label">企业名称</text><text class="row-value">{{j}}</text></view><view class="info-row-item"><text class="row-label">联系人姓名</text><text class="row-value">{{k}}</text></view><view wx:if="{{l}}" class="info-row-item"><text class="row-label">经营地址</text><text class="row-value">{{m}} {{n}} {{o}}</text></view><view wx:if="{{p}}" class="info-row-item"><text class="row-label">提交申请时间</text><text class="row-value">{{q}}</text></view><view wx:if="{{r}}" class="info-row-item"><text class="row-label">最后审核时间</text><text class="row-value">{{s}}</text></view><view wx:if="{{t}}" class="info-row-item flex-col"><text class="row-label margin-bottom-sm">营业执照</text><view class="image-preview-grid"><image wx:for="{{v}}" wx:for-item="file" wx:key="a" src="{{file.b}}" mode="aspectFill" class="preview-img-item" bindtap="{{file.c}}"/></view></view><view wx:if="{{w}}" class="info-row-item flex-col"><text class="row-label margin-bottom-sm">经营场地照片 ({{x}}张)</text><view class="image-preview-grid"><image wx:for="{{y}}" wx:for-item="file" wx:key="a" src="{{file.b}}" mode="aspectFill" class="preview-img-item" bindtap="{{file.c}}"/></view></view></view></view><view class="section guide-card"><view class="section-title">认证后享有哪些权益？</view><view class="guide-steps"><view class="guide-step"><text class="step-num">01</text><view class="step-meta"><text class="step-title">承运商直连</text><text class="step-desc">解锁全部真实承运商，支持按价格、时效多维比较。</text></view></view><view class="guide-step"><text class="step-num">02</text><view class="step-meta"><text class="step-title">担保交易服务</text><text class="step-desc">支持平台担保交易、订单确认和提送车跟踪。</text></view></view></view></view><view class="fixed-footer"><button wx:if="{{z}}" class="primary-btn" bindtap="{{A}}"> 进入首页找车 </button><button wx:elif="{{B}}" class="plain-btn" bindtap="{{C}}"> 刷新审核状态 </button><button wx:else class="primary-btn" bindtap="{{E}}">{{D}}</button></view><miniapp-login-sheet class="r" u-r="loginSheet" bindsuccess="{{G}}" u-i="6aaf0f56-0" bind:__l="__l"/></view>